data.description: Amazing home opportunity with many improvements including beautiful updated LUXURY TILE HARDWOOD FLOORING throughout *NO Carpet*  ENERGY-EFFICIENT WINDOWS to bring in natural lighting. In 2019 ROOF, HVAC, KITCHEN RANGE were replaced. MICROWAVE and DISHWASHER in 2021. The home has CHARM and features lots of storage space, All bedrooms have walk in closets. Located in a desirable neighborhood and nestled in a cul de sac. this 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom home, 2 our-sized living areas, family rm with fireplace, officer or flex space, dining, tall ceilings, wide hallways. Kitchen overlooks dining room. Curl up with a book in the master suite with sitting area. Private backyard has gazebo and shed. Home backs up to a greenbelt. Amenities* On-site Daycare, walking trails, 5 ponds, parks, 2 swimming pools, Minutes from schools, Approximately 20 mins from Dallas, The Shops at Terrell Outlet Mall, and restaurants.FALL in Love and be ready to relax, entertain, walks in the comfort of your NEW Home.
